As you proceed through the first corridor, a memory hits you...

Your taken back to the first time you've encountered the S.T.O.N.E represesntaitives. You nad the rest of your fellow legion of mercenaries agreed to
a meeting between the parties to achieve some "mutual benefit." The job was simple. Get in, get the stones, get out. Simple and easy money. It was all promising at
first, in hindsight a little too promising. A deal was made, and there began the partnership of The Night Raid Mercenaries and S.T.O.N.E Corp. Litttle did I know how
trivial this parnership would turn out...

Use the ls command to look around the corridor room

